{"tid":2448234,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"被控咬斷警手指罪成囚 5 年半　杜啟華入獄前的混沌與日常","createTime":"2021-03-15T18:53:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-16T16:57:08.000Z","uid":391838,"like":26,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"31442528a0fa88f6e2224465f514d8a59e9a783e","tid":2448234,"uid":391838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T18:53:26.000Z","msg":"#立場影像​​​ #杜啟華​ #反送中​<br />\n<br />\n專訪全文：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/38IEsSF​\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F38IEsSF%E2%80%8B&d=HziU8jWK8j2Oa3ZLfTDirC%2B7EDXmwg1SXj7S5MqlT1o%3D&h=cd6f0182\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/38IEsSF​</a><br />\n<br />\n24 歲港大畢業生杜啟華，被指在沙田新城市廣場咬斷警手指，襲警等罪名成立，被判囚 5 年半。杜啟華的案件礙於疫情一拖再拖，審理時間又較原定長了一半。案發至被裁定罪成的 592 日，杜啟華一早已有入獄的心理準備，但借來的自由卻似是沒有終點的倒數，生活和情緒猶如被官司拖進泥沼，仍舊黏糊糊般停滯不前。<br />\n<br />\n與朋友無數次踐行、為母親準備晚餐、考取了健身教練牌照卻沒有用武之地，《立場》紀錄了杜啟華入獄前的一段日子，「係社會逼得我們這一代扭曲成咁」杜啟華這樣總結。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/skMei-qBwA8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FskMei-qBwA8&d=HziU8jWK8j2Oa3ZLfTDirC%2B7EDXmwg1SXj7S5MqlT1o%3D&h=535f18c7\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/skMei-qBwA8</a>"},{"pid":"798debaddf126488db3ec52eaa38310de933adc2","tid":2448234,"uid":214997,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T18:54:48.000Z","msg":"佢條片打定輸數坐四年 <br />\n點知判五年半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10b0c08996d4b159fb3df1b97db6895a95c61cfd","tid":2448234,"uid":391838,"like":14,"dislike":3,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"798debaddf126488db3ec52eaa38310de933adc2","tid":2448234,"uid":214997,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T18:54:48.000Z","msg":"佢條片打定輸數坐四年 <br />\n點知判五年半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T18:58:58.000Z","msg":"五年半<br />\n痴撚線陳同佳都係得兩年半<br />\n我屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62eb667be9534a9fe2c8280bd